casebody.data:
ST. JAMES SCHOOL, Petitioner
v.
Darryl BIEL, as Personal Representative of the Estate of Kristen Biel No. 19-348 Supreme Court of the United States. December 18, 2019

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted. The case is consolidated, and a total of one hour is allotted for oral argument.
